  1456	
  1457	## 16. Known gaps and unwalked cases
  1458	
  1459	No acceptance case or round-4 docket schedule is unwalked.
  1460	
  1461	The remaining gaps are measurements and implementation existence proofs, not
  1462	unstated correctness mechanisms:
  1463	
  1464	- the coarse exact-world gate during long receipt history may fail the React
  1465	  1.10x or typeahead gate;
  1466	- LOGGED-quiet has a previously measured 2.4-3.8% floor against a 2% contract;
  1467	- flattened basis length/value revalidation cost is unmeasured;
  1468	- value-blind fan-out, dense retirement, lock-view copy cost, and registrar
  1469	  wrapper cost are unmeasured;
  1470	- current-generation React implementations of F2 same-root discard ordering,
  1471	  F3 per-root watermarks, and F9 Offscreen publication must be built and pass
  1472	  the fork tests;
  1473	- registrar coverage is intentionally finite. Pre-existing MessagePort
  1474	  listeners, cached original host functions, and unlisted schedulers require
  1475	  ActionScope or native AsyncContext and warn when detectable.
  1476	
  1477	No fallback mechanism is authorized in this consolidation round. A failed
  1478	correctness proof rejects the design; a failed numeric gate rejects the
  1479	design or requires an explicit requirement change.

