    51	## Concurrency architecture facts (from the arena round + re-judgment)
    52	
    53	- React's own model: setState appends lane-tagged updates to per-hook queues;
    54	  renders apply included lanes and rebase the rest; urgent-applied results
    55	  become the base only for *unskipped* prefixes — replay-in-write-order over
    56	  the pre-batch base is the parity-correct fold (C3's 4-not-3 arithmetic).
