    81	## Cost model warnings (paid before, don't repeat)
    82	
    83	- Eager per-write world evaluation on the write path (watcher cutoffs) is
    84	  the expensive shape; kernel-staleness + lazy pull, or memo-shared
    85	  evaluation, are the two known mitigations — price whichever you pick
